<title>SOUTH AFRICA: PGM withdraws cautionary.</title>
<headline>PGM withdraws cautionary.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-06-19</dateline>
<text>
<p>PGM Investments Ltd, the holding company of Vansa Vanadium SA Ltd, said on Thursday talks referred to in May to which the Competitions Board was party had been terminated.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom +27 11 482-1003</p>
